# Personalized News Recommendation System

## 📌 Project Description
The Personalized News Recommendation System suggests news articles to users based on their interests and reading behavior.  
This project uses machine learning techniques to analyze news content and recommend similar articles to improve the user experience.

## 🚀 Features
- Personalized news recommendations
- Content-based filtering
- News similarity analysis
- Simple and efficient recommendation system

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn

